high_descs: Turn left, and walk towards the bathtub.
Grab a dirty rag from inside the bathtub.
Turn around, and walk towards the sink on your left.
Clean the rag in the sink.
Turn around and face the toilet.
Place the rag on top of the toilet.
anns.task_desc: Place a cleaned rag on top of a toilet.

high_descs: Pick up the rag on the right in the tub.
Bring the rag to the sink.
Wash the rag in the sink.
Bring the rag to the toilet.
Put the rag on the toilet tank lid.
anns.task_desc: Put a cleaned rag on the toilet tank lid.

high_descs: take a dirty cloth out of the bathtub
bring the cloth over to the bathroom sink
wash the cloth in the sink
bring the cloth over to the toilet
place the cloth on top of the toilet
anns.task_desc: place a clean cloth on top of the toilet
